headline: IPG Q2 Deep Dive: Strategic Transformation and Omnicom Deal Shape Outlook
summary: Global advertising conglomerate Interpublic Group (NYSE:IPG) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, but sales fell by 6.6% year on year to $2.17 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.75 per share was 33.7% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
